data.description: Welcome to this charming, meticulously maintained CBS home nestled in Lakewood Park. Situated conveniently across from the library and a picturesque lake, this delightful residence offers proximity to the fire department and is within walking distance of the elementary school.Built with care, this home boasts numerous updates: the well and septic were replaced in 2007, while seamless gutters were installed for added convenience. Enjoy modern comforts with upgraded appliances and revel in the fresh ambiance created by brand new flooring and paint, both inside and out.Perfect for families or those who love outdoor gatherings, the property features a spacious fenced-in backyard, providing ample space for relaxation and play.
